A Sample Dataset Based On a Serial Mediation Model With Weak Paths (For Testing)

Source: R/data.R
dat_serial_4_weak.Rd

Generated from a serial mediation model (n = 100).

Usage

dat_serial_4_weak

Format

A data frame with four variables:

x

Predictor

m1

Mediator

m2

Mediator

y

Outcome

Details

The model to be fitted:

m1 ~ x
m2 ~ m1 + x
y  ~ m2 + m1 + x
